                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020217-48-off253 t18020217-48-cd254"></join>, a sheet, value 7s. and a blanket, value 4s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18020217-48-victim596" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
                  Brereton
               <interp inst="t18020217-48-victim596" type="surname" value="Brereton"></interp>
